usage: bean-query FILENAME.beancount balances [-h] [-e FILTER_EXPRESSION] [-c] [--fullnames] [filters [filters ...]]

Print out the trial balance of accounts matching an expression. (aliases: balances,bal,trial; formats: html,htmldiv,text)

positional arguments:
  filters               Filter expression(s) to select the subset of transactions.

optional arguments:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  -e FILTER_EXPRESSION, --filter-expression FILTER_EXPRESSION, --expression FILTER_EXPRESSION, --regexp FILTER_EXPRESSION
                        Filter expression for which account balances to display.
  -c, --at-cost, --cost
                        Render values at cost, convert the units to cost value
  --fullnames           Output full account names.
